{"tid":2397331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp講粗口竟遭刑事起訴　英女被禁離開杜拜並可能判囚兩年","createTime":"2021-02-06T10:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T14:06:56.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"299178f0a1d840377775d3f4ee8d6555eda97ae2","tid":2397331,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n事緣去年10月，英女因為封城要在家工作，並因為使用餐桌問題在WhatsApp與室友爭執，並一度發送「f*** you」的粗口給對方，不料對方就此報警。英女向英國傳媒表示︰「我一生從未捲入過麻煩事，因為一個我與室友的WhatsApp的私人訊息，而被控刑事罪行，令我很震驚&hellip;&hellip;更甚者，這些訊息在數個月前已經發出，卻在現時，當我已把所有物品運走、訂了機票，簽證快過期時，我才知道有這案件。」<br />\n案件令英女目前無法回家，還可能被判入獄及罰款，「我不能相信室友所作的事，她很刻毒，我請求她撤回投訴，但她說『這是刑事罪行』」。她又指室友並不理會她的慘況，「我從未想過一名歐洲人會如此利用阿聯酋國家的嚴厲法例，我們曾住在同一間屋，一直相處得很輕鬆」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210206/UNGXBMC2KFBVJJDZSN7S2A32MI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210206%2FUNGXBMC2KFBVJJDZSN7S2A32MI%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=5370acb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210206%2FUNGXBMC2KFBVJJDZSN7S2A32MI%2F&h=6faf1430\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210206/UNGXBMC2KFBVJJDZSN7S2A32MI/</a>。"},{"pid":"ecad0cab0fdac2959a57d9957fea9727546b03ef","tid":2397331,"uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:35:51.000Z","msg":"傳類召喚"},{"pid":"615e2e21ea3a50e2d7e5e438087fee79695c0e40","tid":2397331,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"超方丈"},{"pid":"8f5918def5fdb462df4f39e3edd1b1e7a396adf9","tid":2397331,"uid":374134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"咁連登個個都會終身監禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />